Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:14.83,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Dawn comes softer than a sleeping breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:23.12,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,0)}Your dream runs through the forest now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:29.89,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,200)}You wake up and stir to find the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:37.65,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If you've lost it, I'll find it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:47.44,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}It's hidden in our future
